Project building steps 

1- Prepar project with important dependencies 
   * Retrofit
   * MVVM (structural design pattern)
   * Recyclerview
   
   
2- Starting preparing packages for good structural
   * data
   * ui
   * model


3- Config Retrofit to make call with API 
   * Create interface
   * Create Clien with our url
   * Config json converter 
  

4- Create models and ViewModel Class to process data
   * Create instance in MainActivity to use
   * Get data from Interface and set in Adapter 


5- Config UI to show data
   * Create RecycllerView
   * Create Adapter to set data in RecycllerView
   

6- Config the Testing section in (Unit Test)
   * Make call to Api for Testing 
   * Check responce status 
 
